text: Masbate City is a city in the Philippines. It is the capital of the province of Masbate. According to the 2020 census, 104,522 people lived there. Masbate City is the only city in the province. It is the province's main commercial center and seaport. The city is on the Masbate Island. Category:Cities in the Philippines Category:Provincial capitals of the Philippines Category:Masbate
title: Masbate City
